{
  "stem": "304.4",
  "chunk_idx": 16,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 9.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And if she was there in a German village-- I didn't know even the name of the village.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "I still don't know.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "If she was there, she had to run away.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "So she had a little taste of war.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And I couldn't make myself-- in spite of my hunger, I couldn't make myself to go up to her and ask for a-- for a-- maybe, maybe she had.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And maybe she would have said she doesn't.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "But I didn't do it.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "So I will never know.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And then we went to this forest.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And they let us stay there.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "They didn't bother us anymore.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "But the hunger was so unbearable that people start to go to the villages to look for food.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "And once a girl disappeared.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "And another time, two girls were shot.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "And they came back, and then one girl died.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "While we were watching, she bled, bled to death.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "And there was nothing we could do, a young girl.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "She was shot in the shin.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "Because-- and the doctor came.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "We found the doctor.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "But there was nothing he could do because he didn't have anything.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "And then the third day, after all this, what was so-- I picked up myself.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "And I said to my group of girls with  whom I was together, I said, I'm going to look for food.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "And they looked at me, you are crazy.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "You saw what happened.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "I said, maybe it will be easier to die from a bullet than from hunger.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "We didn't know how long it will last.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 35,
      "text": "And I said, I'm going.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 36,
      "text": "And nobody would come.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 37,
      "text": "I said, I'm going on my own.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 38,
      "text": "And then one girl stood up.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 39,
      "text": "[DRINKS] I only know that her name was Irene.",
      "word_count": 9
    }
  ],
